Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.qubitekk.CC1, [':ACKN OF', 'FIRM?', ':ACKN ON',
    'CLEA', ':ACKN OF', 'CLEA'], ['', 'Firmware v2.010', 'CLEA', ':ACKN OF'
    ], sep='\n') as cc:
    assert not cc.acknowledge
    cc.acknowledge = True
    assert cc.acknowledge
    cc.clear_counts()
    cc.acknowledge = False
    assert not cc.acknowledge
    cc.clear_counts()
